{"tid":342377,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（勁過武松打虎）單親媽與鯊魚搏鬥 徒手挖眼成功保命","createTime":"2017-07-31T14:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T23:14:33.000Z","uid":41351,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb7734797e5586ece455d9ed717b079b332e8b95","tid":342377,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"真的很偉大！美國一名單親媽媽莉安艾利森（Leeanne Ericson）日前到南加州聖安諾非（San Onofre）一處海灘游泳，未料她在觀看男友衝浪時，卻突然遭到鯊魚攻擊咬住她的腿，使她整個人都被拖入水中，正當她感到絕望之際，想到自己的孩子，於是頓生勇氣，奮力與鯊魚搏鬥，挖出了鯊魚眼睛，因此逃過一劫。<br />\n  據外媒報導，35歲的莉安有一個11歲的女兒以及一對4歲的雙胞胎，今年4月29日她和家人以及男友達斯提（Dusty Phillips）至海邊遊玩，沒想到卻遇上鯊魚攻擊，她的大腿肉被咬掉一大塊，讓她痛不欲生，覺得自己就要魂斷鯊魚之口，然而此時她卻突然想起自己的三個孩子，於是決定放手一搏，和鯊魚拚了！<br />\n<br />\n莉安回憶道：「我試著要推開鯊魚，手剛好碰到牠的眼睛，於是我就開始徒手挖牠的眼窩，感覺很像是在挖果凍。」最後鯊魚總算鬆口讓莉安得以逃脫，而莉安的男友聽見她的慘叫聲卻不見其人影，緊張地到處尋找，終於在不遠處的海中發現載浮載沉的莉安，連忙將她送醫急救。<br />\n<br />\n而歷經8次手術後，莉安目前正積極進行復健，努力讓生活漸漸回歸正常。不過也因為醫療費用負擔相當大，加上此次意外讓她成了殘疾人士，因此失去了子女的撫養權，生活相當困頓，所幸目前網路上正發起募款活動，希望能幫助莉安度過難關，令她相當感動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/為母則強-單親媽遇鯊魚攻擊-徒手勇挖魚眼-034500733.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E7%82%BA%E6%AF%8D%E5%89%87%E5%BC%B7-%E5%96%AE%E8%A6%AA%E5%AA%BD%E9%81%87%E9%AF%8A%E9%AD%9A%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-%E5%BE%92%E6%89%8B%E5%8B%87%E6%8C%96%E9%AD%9A%E7%9C%BC-034500733.html&d=hE3THAwR%2BRpaIiUHAoFHfcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=be41dd35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/為母則強-單親媽遇鯊魚攻擊-徒手勇挖魚眼-034500733.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/222521_d2857856151ee3fd5b6501cfe2633d64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F222521_d2857856151ee3fd5b6501cfe2633d64.jpg&h=92544042&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/222522_b0ccd35742946f6281820030b5197c49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F222522_b0ccd35742946f6281820030b5197c49.jpg&h=de671ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鯊魚就咁盲左一隻眼"},{"pid":"aede98ce05cf6d6aab90eb24d54f077b0ce56568","tid":342377,"uid":53421,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"隻鯊魚好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83104316917a4b558ecb2b77ea2711c8a638b8a","tid":342377,"uid":1487,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"她知道 哭是沒用的"},{"pid":"93487c6ed730a8dc45815e69cdcf6cd3dcb49658","tid":342377,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:32:05.000Z","msg":"留一手好"},{"pid":"14dcb8b94a3c50ec540bd0e636a019210a5fbcd5","tid":342377,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ec2cbffb5388eb5464405145ee8304153bcfc2","tid":342377,"uid":84494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她知道 哭是沒用的</blockquote><br />\n我來挖！"},{"pid":"e4a17b21db4cf131a8edc86d05430b13e94fe6d0","tid":342377,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7634d9fcdc58318bbb2ad22c97e6868b587eec8","tid":342377,"uid":15538,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"不要低頭 眼珠會掉下來"},{"pid":"bf26d1a6bd8b92231f066f04bc7c0b9865b047ad","tid":342377,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"隻鯊魚玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8679c928c18ff526d0ce474d2c1deca5604fb61","tid":342377,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/224209_71e5a4bc35d727549aee528eb1355c8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t